subject: Auto insurance quotes
body:
Want
                to save on your auto insurance?
      The cost of auto insurance coverage for the same person can vary enormously
      - in some cases, by more than $2,000 per year, from company to company.
      Click here to
      shop and compare.
                  It will only take 2 minutes
        That's all it takes to answer a few questions, and you'll get side-by-side
          quotes from leading
        companies-all at once.
